<body><div type="diplomatic"><pb facs="#facs_555" id="276v"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee"><ab facs="#facs_555_r2l9">Dem veſten Hannſen von Rebıcʒ </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_555_r2l10">amptman ʒu Staffelſteın </ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content"><note place="marginleft"><ab facs="#facs_555_r1l1"><expan>ſ<ex>i</ex>n<ex>e</ex></expan> <expan>ſ<ex>er</ex>uicıo</expan> </ab></note>
<ab facs="#facs_555_r2l11">Hanns von Rebıcʒ als Jr vns <expan>verſchr<ex>iben</ex></expan> habt / eẅch ſey geſagt wie </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_555_r2l12">dıe <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>n</expan> nach eẅch <expan>geſtande<ex>n</ex></expan> haben etc das <expan>habe<ex>n</ex></expan> wır wol <expan>vernom<ex>en</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_555_r2l13">Nu . als Nıkel lang / Vns vnd dıe <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>n</expan> <expan>manıgfeltıkl<ex>ich</ex></expan> rawbot vnd </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_555_r2l14">beſchedıgot on ſchult vnd on ſache . Ʒu <expan>denſelbe<ex>n</ex></expan> <expan>ʒeıte<ex>n</ex></expan> ward vns </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_555_r2l15">vermeldt / wıe Jm einr <expan>genan<ex>n</ex>t</expan> Hanns von Rebıcʒ mıtſampt <expan>and<ex>er</ex>n</expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_555_r2l16"><expan>geholff<ex>en</ex></expan> hett den <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>n</expan> das Jr alſo rewplıch <expan>ʒuneme<ex>n</ex></expan> / Ob Jr der = </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_555_r2l17">ſelb hanns von Rebıcʒ ſeyt <expan>od<ex>er</ex></expan> niht / das müſʒt ır <expan>wıſſ<ex>en</ex></expan> . Nu <expan>wölte<ex>n</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_555_r2l18">wir <expan>vng<ex>er</ex>n</expan> nach <expan>yema<ex>n</ex>t</expan> <expan>geſtande<ex>n</ex></expan> <expan>habe<ex>n</ex></expan> / der vns <expan>od<ex>er</ex></expan> den <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>n</expan> niht </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_555_r2l19">getan hett / <expan>Hett<ex>en</ex></expan> wır <expan>ab<ex>er</ex></expan> nach dem <expan>vorg<ex>enanten</ex></expan> Nıkel <expan>lange<ex>n</ex></expan> vnd <expan>and<ex>er</ex>n</expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_555_r2l20">dıe Jm <expan>wıd<ex>er</ex></expan> vns alſo <expan>geholff<ex>en</ex></expan> <expan>habe<ex>n</ex></expan> . <expan>muge<ex>n</ex></expan> ſteen . das <expan>w<ex>er</ex>e</expan> <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex></expan> vnd </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_555_r2l21">der <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>n</expan> notdurft <expan>geweſ<ex>en</ex></expan> / Vnd als Jr in <expan>eẅ<ex>r</ex>m</expan> <expan>br<ex>ief</ex></expan> meldt / vvıe Jr </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_555_r2l22"><expan>wıd<ex>er</ex></expan> vns niht getan habt / VVölt Jr <expan>daru<ex>m</ex>b</expan> <expan>hıeʒwıſch<ex>en</ex></expan> ſand thomas </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_555_r2l23">tag . <expan>ſchıerıſtkünft<ex>ig</ex></expan> ʒu vns <expan>kome<ex>n</ex></expan> . So ſüllt Jr ʒu vnd von vns </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_555_r2l24">für vns vnd dıe <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>n</expan> on <expan>geu<ex>er</ex>de</expan> vnd bey vns für <expan>all<ex>er</ex>menıkl<ex>ich</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_555_r2l25">drey tag geleyt <expan>habe<ex>n</ex></expan> / alſdenn wellen wır eẅr rede <expan>g<ex>er</ex>n</expan> hören </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_555_r2l26"><expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan> <expan>f<ex>er</ex>ıa</expan> vȷ<hi rend="sup">a</hi></ab>
</div>
</div><div type="regularised"><pb facs="#facs_555" id="276v"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee">
<ab>Dem vesten Hannsen von Rebicz, amptman zu Staffelstein </ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content"><ab><app>
<note place="marginleft">
<expan>S<ex>i</ex>n<ex>e</ex></expan>
<expan>s<ex>er</ex>vicio</expan>. </note>
</app>Hanns von Rebicz, als ir uns
                                                  <expan>verschr<ex>iben</ex></expan> habt, ewch sey
                                                gesagt, wie die <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan> nach
                                                ewch <expan>gestande<ex>n</ex></expan> haben etc.,
                                                das <expan>habe<ex>n</ex></expan> wir wol
                                                  <expan>vernom<ex>en</ex></expan>. Nu, als Nikel
                                                Lang uns und die <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>manigfeltikl<ex>ich</ex></expan> rawbot und
                                                beschedigot on schult und on sache, zu
                                                  <expan>denselbe<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>zeite<ex>n</ex></expan> ward uns vermeldt,
                                                wie im einr, <expan>genan<ex>n</ex>t</expan> Hanns
                                                von Rebicz, mitsampt <expan>and<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>geholff<ex>en</ex></expan> hett, den
                                                  <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan> das ir also
                                                rewplich <expan>zu neme<ex>n</ex></expan>; ob ir
                                                derselb Hanns von Rebicz seyt
                                                  <expan>od<ex>er</ex></expan> niht, das müszt ir
                                                  <expan>wiss<ex>en</ex></expan>. Nu
                                                  <expan>wölte<ex>n</ex></expan> wir
                                                  <expan>ung<ex>er</ex>n</expan> nach
                                                  <expan>yema<ex>n</ex>t</expan>
<expan>gestande<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>habe<ex>n</ex></expan>, der uns
                                                  <expan>od<ex>er</ex></expan> den
                                                  <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan> niht getan hett;
                                                  <expan>hett<ex>en</ex></expan> wir
                                                  <expan>ab<ex>er</ex></expan> nach dem
                                                  <expan>vorg<ex>enanten</ex></expan> Nikel
                                                  <expan>Lange<ex>n</ex></expan> und
                                                  <expan>and<ex>er</ex>n</expan>, die im
                                                  <expan>wid<ex>er</ex></expan> uns also
                                                  <expan>geholff<ex>en</ex></expan>
<expan>habe<ex>n</ex></expan>,
                                                  <expan>muge<ex>n</ex></expan> steen, das
                                                  <expan>w<ex>er</ex>e</expan>
<expan>uns<ex>er</ex></expan> und der
                                                  <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan> notdurft
                                                  <expan>gewes<ex>en</ex></expan>; und als ir in
                                                  <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>m</expan>
<expan>br<ex>ief</ex></expan> meldt, wie ir
                                                  <expan>wid<ex>er</ex></expan> uns niht getan habt,
                                                wölt ir <expan>daru<ex>m</ex>b</expan>
<expan>hiezwisch<ex>en</ex></expan> <app><note><q type="date">sand Thomas tag
    <expan>schieristkünft<ex>ig</ex></expan></q>21.12.1422</note></app> zu uns
                                                  <expan>kome<ex>n</ex></expan>, so süllt ir zu und
                                                von uns für uns und die
                                                  <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan> on
                                                  <expan>gev<ex>er</ex>de</expan> und bey uns für
                                                  <expan>all<ex>er</ex>menikl<ex>ich</ex></expan>
                                                drey tag geleyt <expan>habe<ex>n</ex></expan>,
                                                alsdenn wellen wir ewr rede
                                                  <expan>g<ex>er</ex>n</expan> hören.
                                                  <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan>
<expan>f<ex>er</ex>ia</expan> vi<hi rend="sup">a</hi>. </ab></div>
